    <innerclass refid="structiceberg_1_1CounterResult" prot="public">iceberg::CounterResult</innerclass>
    <innerclass refid="structiceberg_1_1TimerResult" prot="public">iceberg::TimerResult</innerclass>
    <innernamespace refid="namespaceiceberg">iceberg</innernamespace>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Serialisable snapshot types shared across scan and commit metrics. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>CounterResult, TimerResult, and DurationNs are primitive result types used by ScanMetricsResult, CommitMetricsResult, and the JSON serde layer. Defining them here keeps ScanReport and CommitReport headers independent of each other. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
